playActionNow 
Game: ARMA 2  (1.00) 
Description: When used on a person, a smooth transition to the given action will 
 be initiated, but all previous playAction are discarded. Unlike 
 playAction, playActionNow is automatically executed on all clients 
.  
Syntax:  
 soldier playActionNow action 
Parameters: 
soldier: Object - 
action: String - 
Return Value: 
 Nothing